ESTATE OF Patricia M. QUINN, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Michael F. QUINN (Deceased), Defendant. (Marita Quinn-Petitioner) C-327 September Term 2017
079877 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 17, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001490-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
